Rubio, for his part, has defended the USAID cuts, but there are early worri=
es that
he=E2=80=99s being undercut by Trump and Trump=E2=80=99s team in other area=
s. Rubio, for instance, scored a big diplomatic win against China when he m=
et with Panamanian president Jos=C3=A9 Ra=C3=BAl Mulino on his first intern=
ational trip as secretary of state this past weekend: Shortly after the mee=
ting, Mulino announced that Panama would not renew its participation in Chi=
na=E2=80=99s Belt and Road Initiative, a massive infrastructure program. Bu=
t just hours later, Trump again threatened to =E2=80=9Ctake back=E2=80=9D
the Panama Canal, antagonizing Panama once more and enfeebling his secretar=
y=E2=80=99s work.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

Meanwhile, even though two of Rubio=E2=80=99s top aides=E2=80=94Michael Nee=
dham and Dan Holler=E2=80=94followed him to State, there are concerns that =
he isn=E2=80=99t getting his people through the White House=E2=80=99s Presi=
dential Personnel Office, which oversees hiring within the administration. =
(A State Department aide
said there are a lot of complaints about the slow hiring process, but noted=
 that it=E2=80=99s not unique to State or Rubio.) Republican and Democratic=
 critics alike point to the hiring of two Trump loyalists at State, Pete Ma=
rocco and Darren Beattie, as potential hindrances to Rubio.

Marocco, who worked at the Commerce, Defense, and State Departments as well=
 as USAID during Trump=E2=80=99s first term, has faced
accusations ( https://www.politico.com/news/2020/09/22/usaid-dissent-memo-t=
rump-420153?utm_campaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F=
5%2F25%29&utm_content=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F5%2=
F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c606=
17da42abd12a ) of creating confusing and toxic work environments. USAID per=
sonnel sent a dissent memo about Marocco just three months after he joined =
the agency in 2020. Meanwhile, Beattie, a former speechwriter from Trump=E2=
=80=99s first term who was fired after CNN
reported ( https://www.cnn.com/2025/02/03/politics/kfile-darren-beattie-sta=
