 ) his attendance at a white nationalist conference, has been named acting =
secretary of state for public diplomacy and public affairs.

Beattie also has a trail of racist, misogynistic, and January 6-supporting =
social media posts, and according to Semafor and CNN, founded the
far-right, Trump-supporting outlet Revolver. (Revolver somehow got an exclu=
